# 🏀 Adidas US Sales Analysis Dashboard  

This project explores Adidas US retail performance data — highlighting key trends in revenue, profitability, and sales across channels and regions.  

## 📊 Interactive Dashboard  
Click below to view the live interactive dashboard hosted on Microsoft Fabric 👇  

👉 [**View Dashboard on Power BI**](https://app.fabric.microsoft.com/reportEmbed?reportId=00994adb-de07-47fa-97c6-77465ed13b7d&autoAuth=true&ctid=37d7521a-5079-48af-9131-4ac2cb6f1e3a)

